  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/453e6e2eedee95788bf86900abfbb44a.poster.avif?t=1601870279\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/453e6e2eedee95788bf86900abfbb44a.webm?t=1601870279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/453e6e2eedee95788bf86900abfbb44a.mp4?t=1601870279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you Ready to Swing? This upcoming first-person platformer very much has the visual appeal and sheer electricity of gameplay.   As for its mechanics, it will feature swinging via grapple, jumping, and wall-running, all of which are set in an amazing neo-lit world. Early Access Includes Full playable game and training area for you to further explore your skills.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/005a638761015f2262bf1089cfc1d99c.poster.avif?t=1601870279\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/005a638761015f2262bf1089cfc1d99c.webm?t=1601870279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424120/extras/005a638761015f2262bf1089cfc1d99c.mp4?t=1601870279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
